      <title>瀚亚、霸菱在中国缩减对冲基金团队</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-05/eastspring-barings-shrink-hedge-fund-teams-in-china-pullback</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瀚亚投资 (Eastspring Investments) 和巴林银行 (Barings LLC) 一直在中国对冲基金业务部门裁员，突显出全球资产管理公司在 6 万亿元人民币（合 8,400 亿美元）的本土市场中站稳脚跟所面临的挑战。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-05/eastspring-barings-shrink-hedge-fund-teams-in-china-pullback</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 05 Dec 2023 00:57:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>BYD, Netease, Luzhou Laojiao Favored, Morningstar Says</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2023-12-05/byd-netease-luzhou-laojiao-favored-morningstar-says-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[晨星公司亚洲股票研究总监 Lorraine Tan 讨论了美国经济前景、美联储政策及其对金融市场的影响。她还谈到了她在中国看到的机遇。她在“彭博黎明：亚洲”节目中与海迪·斯特劳德-瓦茨和雪莉·安交谈。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2023-12-05/byd-netease-luzhou-laojiao-favored-morningstar-says-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 05 Dec 2023 00:35:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
